## AI RESPONSE FORMAT

During Phases 1, 2, and 3 every response follows this structure. No exceptions.

```
Understood: [One sentence reflecting exactly what the user said — specific, not paraphrased]
Question: "[One question. Never two. Ends with a question mark.]"
```

The AIResponseBlock component enforces this structurally. It does not render without both parts.

