## WHAT NOT TO BUILD IN V1

Do not build these regardless of how good they sound in the moment.

- ❌ ExpertPanel functionality (LegiScan + CongressMCP) — icon present, functionality is v1.5
- ❌ Authentication and user accounts — anonymous sessions only
- ❌ Author attribution on drafts — v1.5
- ❌ Viability score algorithm — placeholder percentage, real algorithm is v2
- ❌ Prediction markets
- ❌ Automated contact routing — manual routing by Andrew is v1. Automation is v2.
- ❌ Institutional accounts for policymakers/product teams — v1.5 goal
- ❌ Comments on drafts
- ❌ Mobile app

**v1 is:** Conversation → 7 slots → Draft → Publish → Manual routing by admin → Feed → Upvote → Vote threshold re-send. Nothing else.

